OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775170979
OL,3,CFifa criticised for 'ridiculous'
OL,4,C#8,000 World Cup final tickets
OL,6,FFifa has been criticised for its
OL,7,F"ridiculous" pricing policies, as a
OL,8,Fticket for the World Cup final was
OL,9,Fpriced at over #8,300 in the final
OL,10,Fsale before the tournament begins this
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FThe final sales window opened on
OL,14,FWednesday with fans around the world
OL,15,Freporting lengthy delays in accessing
OL,16,Fthe tickets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
