OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775170979
OL,3,CFifa criticised for 'ridiculous'
OL,4,C#8,000 World Cup final tickets
OL,6,FFifa has faced criticism over the
OL,7,Fpricing of tickets since launching
OL,8,Finitial sales last autumn, and over
OL,9,Fthe decision to adopt dynamic pricing,
OL,10,Fwhere costs rise or fall depending on
OL,11,Fdemand.
OL,13,FIt has led to uproar among fans and
OL,14,Fcriticism of the nations hosting the
OL,15,Ftournament, Canada, the USA and Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
