CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775170979
OL,3,CFifa criticised for 'ridiculous'
OL,4,C#8,000 World Cup final tickets
OL,6,FThe Athletic reported tickets for
OL,7,Froughly 40 of the 104 matches were
OL,8,Fmore expensive than they had been in
OL,9,Fprevious sales windows, and found a
OL,10,FCategory 1 ticket for the final was
OL,11,Fnow costing almost $11,000 (#8,335) up
OL,12,Ffrom less than $7,000 (#5,288) in the
OL,13,Ffirst window.
OL,15,FEven that initial price was way above
OL,16,Fthe figure quoted in the co-hosts' bid
OL,17,Fbook submitted to FIFA, which pledged
OL,18,Fthat a Category 1 ticket for the final
OL,19,Fwould cost 1,550 US dollars (#1,173).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
