FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775170979
OL,3,CFifa criticised for 'ridiculous'
OL,4,C#8,000 World Cup final tickets
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Football
OL,7,FSupporters' Association said on
OL,8,FThursday: "This is the most expensive
OL,9,FWorld Cup in history for travelling
OL,10,Fsupporters, from match tickets to
OL,11,Ftravel and accommodation. It isn't
OL,12,Fjust an issue for English fans but for
OL,13,Fthose across the planet.
OL,15,F"Fifa's ridiculous ticket pricing and
OL,16,Fopaque policies have led many fans to
OL,17,Fconclude they simply can't afford to
OL,18,Fattend football's greatest global
OL,19,Fevent."
OL,26,@pD@KOUwD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
