PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775170979
OL,3,CFifa criticised for 'ridiculous'
OL,4,C#8,000 World Cup final tickets
OL,6,FLast week, Football Supporters Europe
OL,7,F(FSE) lodged a complaint over Fifa's
OL,8,FWorld Cup ticket pricing strategy with
OL,9,Fthe European Commission.
OL,11,FThere were also reports of long queues
OL,12,Fjust to gain access to the sales
OL,13,Fplatform, and supporters being sent
OL,14,Fdown a queue intended only for fans in
OL,15,Floyalty schemes for the countries who
OL,16,Fsealed qualification on Tuesday.
OL,18,FFifa has been contacted for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
